# 1. Introduction

Prefix Sum is one of the most important preprocessing techniques in Data Structures and Algorithms.

It allows us to answer range sum queries efficiently.

Many medium and hard interview problems become easy once you identify the Prefix Sum pattern.

---

# Why Learn Prefix Sum?

Used in:

- Range Sum Queries
- Subarray Problems
- Continuous Sum Problems
- Count Subarrays
- HashMap Problems
- Binary Array Problems
- Matrix Sum Problems
- Competitive Programming
- FAANG Interviews

