# 16. Prefix XOR

Variation of Prefix Sum.

Formula:

```java
prefixXor[i]
=
prefixXor[i-1] ^ arr[i];
```

---

Range XOR

```java
prefixXor[R]
^
prefixXor[L-1]
```

---

Interview Favorite.

