# 17. 2D Prefix Sum

Matrix:

```text
1 2 3

4 5 6

7 8 9
```

---

Formula

```java
prefix[i][j]
=
matrix[i][j]
+
prefix[i-1][j]
+
prefix[i][j-1]
-
prefix[i-1][j-1];
```

---

Visualization

