# 18. Difference Array + Prefix Sum

Advanced Pattern

Used for:

```text
Range Updates
```

Instead of updating every element.

---

Update:

```java
diff[L] += val;

diff[R+1] -= val;
```

---

After all updates:

```java
Take Prefix Sum
```

Recover final array.

---

Complexity

```text
O(1)
```

per update.

