# 20. Common Mistakes

---

## Mistake 1

Forgetting

```java
map.put(0,1);
```

This misses subarrays starting from index 0.

---

## Mistake 2

Wrong Formula

Wrong:

```java
prefix[L] - prefix[R]
```

Correct:

```java
prefix[R] - prefix[L-1]
```

---

## Mistake 3

Modulo Negative Values

Use:

```java
mod = ((prefix % k) + k) % k;
```

---

## Mistake 4

Integer Overflow

Use:

```java
long prefix;
```

when constraints are large.

